{"tid":2259420,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–武漢肺炎病毒D614G變種","createTime":"2020-10-26T23:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T10:19:53.000Z","uid":38861,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"34006279a6117c17e6ce67824f15a3c185f39cb0","tid":2259420,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T23:18:30.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎病毒現時的主流品種為D614G，一道較為簡易的說明方法就是原來的D614品種變異成為G614品種。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oxk8EN9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOxk8EN9.jpg&h=9d4c664e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而根據GISAID公開資料庫記錄，G614品種最先在1月24日的四川病毒樣本出現。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）何解G614品種能夠成為主流，一直是科學家想解答的問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1xiY11x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1xiY11x.jpg&h=f456bc79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前所獲得的實驗數據，大多是從病毒一小段的部份、或者是合成病毒獲取結果，沒能百分百反映現實。<br />\n<br />\n直至最近，才有科學家利用真實存在的武肺病毒進行實驗。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）在研究中（Ref1)，科學家將D614品種及G614品種以1 : 1的比例從倉鼠的鼻孔注入其體內。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/31mS6th.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F31mS6th.jpg&h=c4ebec76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果最終G614品種/D614品種的比例大於1的話，亦即是代表G614品種在繁殖方面比D614品種更為優勝。<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）倉鼠受病毒感染7日後，鼻孔、氣管及肺部個別區域的G614品種/D614品種均大於1，顯示G614品種在上述區域有著較佳的繁殖優勢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/upjYhz1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FupjYhz1.png&h=d357248e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時在實驗室的人體肺部細胞中，就算用上D614品種及G614品種以9 : 1的比例方式感染，G614品種/D614品種在其後感染日子均呈大於1的狀態，更進一步顯示G614品種的繁殖優勢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖5）科學家同時亦發現，G614品種的病毒在各種溫度上均比D614品種相對為穩定。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3f5P8GL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3f5P8GL.png&h=1a533fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過好消息是，對抗D614品種的抗體，其對抗G614品種品種效率並無任何損傷。<br />\n<br />\n這亦即間接顯示出以D614品種作原材料的疫苗，其產生的抗體亦能有效對抗G614品種病毒，而事實上現今亦有疫苗是利用G614品種作原材料，奈何是鄰國出品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖6）至於近來在挪威發現的新變種M439K品種，基於是新發現的關係，現時醫學界及學術界均無任何學術文章作詳細研究其特性。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X0L4Xz9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX0L4Xz9.png&h=c31e810c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n莫論病毒變種與否，只需一個乞嗤，病毒就已經不需近距離接觸，便能透過體液傳播至他人。<br />\n<br />\n將「新變種」及「不需近距離接觸」串連在一起的報導手法，有著混淆視聽的成份，並不可取。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=2a12874d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=6e16c634\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=8c5d881a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2895-3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41586-020-2895-3&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=7ef6cabf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2895-3</a>"},{"pid":"0b6b30714e610efcdaf8983620fb452c326e3e62","tid":2259420,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T23:26:31.000Z","msg":"所以話 RNA病毒係咪根本冇準確疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c0d76ccd44b56c635a2ff9e764a9cd5d243584","tid":2259420,"uid":66044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T23:31:00.000Z","msg":"如果變種速度咁快 有咩可以搞呢 一年已經有咁多變種 好似流感病毒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bceded9a6e36d166582c6338d7b3d169d8a122","tid":2259420,"uid":38861,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"65c0d76ccd44b56c635a2ff9e764a9cd5d243584","tid":2259420,"uid":66044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T23:31:00.000Z","msg":"如果變種速度咁快 有咩可以搞呢 一年已經有咁多變種 好似流感病毒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T23:46:35.000Z","msg":"現今解決問題的大方向就係針對兩個唔同部位，希望唔會同時在兩個部位發生的變異會導致到抗體辨認唔到。<br />\n又或者用整個武肺病毒作疫苗原材料，增加辨認病毒不同位置的抗體，但有機會弄巧反拙，詳情之前有打過文章提及:<br />\n<br />\n深入淺出&ndash;中國兩隻臨床Phase3中疫苗的潛在反效果<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2161912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2161912</a>"},{"pid":"5cf1fcfbe7e3de2ff1c829ca66c830b20105df8f","tid":2259420,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T23:51:58.000Z","msg":"正皮<br />\n樓主間唔中就有佳作"},{"pid":"adf80298edb10be0fa592ce9ec319ab251ca9926","tid":2259420,"uid":141655,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T00:19:25.000Z","msg":"連登仔:恐懼撚！1cm！<img src=\"/assets