":"莫論病毒變種與否，只需一個乞嗤，病毒就已經不需近距離接觸，便能透過體液傳播至他人。<br />\n<br />\n早兩日仲見到個廢中拉底個口罩大大聲聲打乞嗤<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:28:27.000Z","msg":"坐低啱啱叫咗個餐/個餐食到一半<br />\n對面或隔離條友狂咳或打大乞痴<br />\n點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:48:37.000Z","msg":"巴打我地亞博見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3436c44deb62bd9016419fed8cb328c798583269","tid":2259420,"uid":133709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T02:47:10.000Z","msg":"巴打 好勁 支持支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ec04898c4bb5cb93876a4207dae95bf2c45363","tid":2259420,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42c4eabc4f1967ce1d7b638985b2384dc5f2d894","tid":2259420,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T01:13:19.000Z","msg":"到底武肺會好似天花咁絕種，定係好似流感咁年年有唔同品種爆發？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"天花會消失係因為佢只係屬於人類嘅病毒<br />\n所以不能斷絕嘅病毒共通點係人畜共患病 <br />\n我地可以隔離或治療所有人<br />\n但我地唔可以隔離或治療所有野生動物 例如 蝙蝠"}]}